http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/RINL-confident-of-a-promising-year-ahead/article14022543.ece

Rashtriya Ispat Nigam Limited, the corporate entity of Visakhapatnam Steel Plant, feels that 2016 offers a lot of promises for the Navratna company.In his Republic Day address at Ukkunagaram, RINL Chairman-cum-Managing Director P. Madhusudan termed 2016 a very promising year for RINL as micro-economic indicators were showing signs of improvement. He highlighted the need to display extraordinary commitment and dedication to improve the bottom line and progress on a sustainable growth path.He observed that some of the crucial areas to enhance the performance during 2016 include increasing volume of operations with right product-mix and higher percentage of value-added steels.